{"tid":627063,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"天水圍天瑞邨麥當勞殺人案，警再拘三名疑犯","createTime":"2018-04-12T15:52:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-12T22:19:12.000Z","uid":17008,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6d5e534b49ee93592c5769bc90e480ffa42d58ea","tid":627063,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1204837/org/1908057efdabd8229045187227f16f86.jpg/5pJmZ1cJnHImRcgN1OcAg7wftz4FOo9XJ2sttydrLbc?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1204837%2Forg%2F1908057efdabd8229045187227f16f86.jpg%2F5pJmZ1cJnHImRcgN1OcAg7wftz4FOo9XJ2sttydrLbc%3Fv%3Dw640&h=080bc21f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方押送三名謀殺案疑犯到天瑞邨麥當勞案情重組。為防疑犯有所舉動，其鞋帶被解下。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1204824/org/c11d4fa52cbe35b7f7d719543fa47322.jpg/l2Y1OsXoaiQa1AwHuVnbgwWuiaXWedT6OYW2MzmFtjM?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1204824%2Forg%2Fc11d4fa52cbe35b7f7d719543fa47322.jpg%2Fl2Y1OsXoaiQa1AwHuVnbgwWuiaXWedT6OYW2MzmFtjM%3Fv%3Dw640&h=7d1352b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1204823/org/dff3be995861eb06def6fd4045540da2.jpg/zeH8Ehwq1H3DWDRSHQi8v7XKMwtl6ueXV6lUH1epVB8?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1204823%2Forg%2Fdff3be995861eb06def6fd4045540da2.jpg%2FzeH8Ehwq1H3DWDRSHQi8v7XKMwtl6ueXV6lUH1epVB8%3Fv%3Dw640&h=05eebad1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1204829/org/c0db1cb9193d32205e8e4289cbe90ed4.jpg/T8A0ZnQvuYCZp5sZsvq32sP0r3ZXnqGZv9U-07_VPtM?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1204829%2Forg%2Fc0db1cb9193d32205e8e4289cbe90ed4.jpg%2FT8A0ZnQvuYCZp5sZsvq32sP0r3ZXnqGZv9U-07_VPtM%3Fv%3Dw640&h=9587eee6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1205542/org/6e3b9fab983e0195303be096a680328a.jpg/-yMjRsQz_LtFGMf0vQvJQsqbncUJV49wtEcZO7RHGTs?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1205542%2Forg%2F6e3b9fab983e0195303be096a680328a.jpg%2F-yMjRsQz_LtFGMf0vQvJQsqbncUJV49wtEcZO7RHGTs%3Fv%3Dw640&h=5ef92a7d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1205543/org/68fd2227de9db1f1ca957c3eb7938134.jpg/OGqXMRKPZ6S4Q90oV69bcE9RU4PZ19ggHRsPKB0bDyg?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1205543%2Forg%2F68fd2227de9db1f1ca957c3eb7938134.jpg%2FOGqXMRKPZ6S4Q90oV69bcE9RU4PZ19ggHRsPKB0bDyg%3Fv%3Dw640&h=18e3ef50&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1205005/org/8f9c7999d6d46d08cccc546f41567fcf.jpg/2yWIqJlrbOvi9L_iTOAoINVUnVfP8Q9ciTdD44k3Q-M?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1205005%2Forg%2F8f9c7999d6d46d08cccc546f41567fcf.jpg%2F2yWIqJlrbOvi9L_iTOAoINVUnVfP8Q9ciTdD44k3Q-M%3Fv%3Dw640&h=b7f1e851&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n謀殺案漏網之魚，十年後終於落網。警方在天水圍天瑞邨麥當勞，就2008年10月一宗謀殺案進行案情重組。快餐店為配合警方調查案件，貼出告示指暫時關閉至下午一時重開。三名疑犯涉嫌在十年前在店內取武器，合共9人圍毆25歲男子潘嘉恩致死。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n十年前天瑞邨麥當勞命案，警方再拘捕三名疑犯，今（13日）由元朗重案二隊押至現場案情重組。疑犯黑布蒙頭，雙手扣上鎖鏈，由警員逐一押進天瑞邨麥當勞。每人逗留約半小時。快餐店貼出告示，指為配合警方調查案件，會暫時關閉至下午一時重開。其中一名疑犯，穿著的波鞋被收起鞋帶，相信是防止被捕人士自殘。據了解，三人在犯案後，潛逃回內地，在內地涉及毒品案件被捕，服刑後，內地公安將三人移交給香港警察。<br />\n<br />\n2008年10月2日，天水圍天瑞邨麥當勞發生謀殺案。一名25歲育有兩女的男子潘嘉恩，在天瑞邨麥當勞遭九名男子圍毆。九男用金屬垃圾棒及雨傘架等作為武器，其中兩人囚終身，另有兩人因誤殺罪判囚4年及5年半。當時五人在逃，警方在十年後，拘捕在逃其中三人，稍後進行案情重組。麥當勞延至兩時許回復正常營業，十年過去，內部已經重新裝修，不見遮架等物品。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1205009/org/1dcd42d93d4b8ddd734e7d655ba2623e.jpg/VqsHWvXW_fI-drzZ-N5KX7WNWigL7L9MBd0waQXdMGk?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1205009%2Forg%2F1dcd42d93d4b8ddd734e7d655ba2623e.jpg%2FVqsHWvXW_fI-drzZ-N5KX7WNWigL7L9MBd0waQXdMGk%3Fv%3Dw640&h=cfff1831&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方準備假人模擬犯罪情況。<br />\n<br />\n天瑞邨街坊表示，夜間有時可見類似童黨的青年，但天恩邨比較多，認為十年來，治安也有改善。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/1204734/org/f908359b413d86321b79f40f5a5115bc.jpg/EAfAw89AJw8U2KYZ5fzRFFeNA-C5GzVYTfczkE33M5A?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1204734%2Forg%2Ff908359b413d86321b79f40f5a5115bc.jpg%2FEAfAw89AJw8U2KYZ5fzRFFeNA-C5GzVYTfczkE33M5A%3Fv%3Dw640&h=8d48fbfa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方在天水圍天瑞邨麥當勞，就2008年10月一宗謀殺案進行案情重組。"},{"pid":"7c0048483fe8c5dd850c7fbe3c7f0ff99d4985da","tid":627063,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:53:16.000Z","msg":"阿差破案，十年未晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1d0ecca078516d58522014d9aa5475fb73de71","tid":627063,"uid":39601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T15:54:24.000Z","msg":"仲有2個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d0854e998465fe98e4c40ea7e6d4061aaad1a83","tid":627063,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"頂你間野都已經裝修過n次仲重組到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"440d66180f4742552c648c47fa46443c5d5e4578","tid":627063,"uid":71676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d0854e998465fe98e4c40ea7e6d4061aaad1a83","tid":627063,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:42:26.000Z","msg":"頂你間野都已經裝修過n次仲重組到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-12T16:44:31.000Z","msg":"形式上重組姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebde1dce766c5391096ced569b9a729242caa235","tid":627063,"uid":57394,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score